Package org.bukkit.attributes

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AttributeFactory
    Provides access to built-in Attributes and creation of AttributeModifiers.
    AttributeModifier
    A numerical transformation that can be applied to the values of Attributes.
    AttributeOwner
    Something that has values for Attributes and is affected by them.
    AttributeValue
    The state of a particular Attribute for a particular LivingEntity, consisting of a base value and a set of AttributeModifiers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Attribute
    An Attribute defines some effect on LivingEntitys that is controlled by a numeric parameter.

    Attributes.Zombie
